    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 wide-body, featuring a 3.6L flat-six equipped with VarioCam Plus. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle with a recently refreshed clutch and a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit. The chassis retains its factory-spec Turbo-derived suspension and 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers, offering exceptional thermal management and lateral stability. The hydraulic steering rack provides unfiltered feedback, and the viscous-coupling AWD system ensures optimal torque distribution. With flawless paint depth and a cabin free of soft-touch degradation, this C4S is a mechanically sorted, turn-key masterpiece for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2022 Luxury Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service history available. Inspect in person.",
      "price": 43500.0,
