    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with deep, mirror-like paint clarity, free of any stone chips, swirls, or door dings. It has been professionally ceramic-coated and kept in a climate-controlled garage under a bespoke soft cover. The interior is equally pristine; the high-grade leather upholstery remains supple with no visible bolster wear, and the cabin still retains that signature new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, having never seen rain or salt. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a 'time capsule' example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
