      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a level of preservation rarely seen on the secondary market, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards for performance and reliability. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than the finest, this specimen offers an unparalleled ownership opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
